remarks.para: This enumeration allows the output stream to write HTML mark up, along with HTML server controls, in response to a Web request.

summary.para: Specifies the HTML tags that can be passed to an or object output stream.
The DHTML rt element, which specifies text for the ruby element.
The string passed as an HTML tag is not recognized.
